Class State

  • java.lang.Object
    • State
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<State>

    public class State
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<State>
    This class is used when creating objects of the State type. It also implements Comparable which is used for compareTo in the compareTo method.
